name: Me myself and I
description: I love reading, but I never do it at home. I’ve seen almost every movie in thriller genre. I used to do beer reviews 'cause I love beer. I would turn into a toad and pee on everybody out of spite. I watched «sex in the city» more than 5 times and Harry Potter more than 20 times. I love Rinata Litvinova and Gaspar Noe. I hate racists and sexists and anyone who can’t see «past their nose».
